Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Client
    Client side of the peer.He knows where to send and receive messages(get,put and delete + results).
    Connection
    Connection class to make a connection with a peer.We give port, name and ip and connection list, and it waits 15 seconds to be sure that peer is online and then creates a socket and puts it in the connections list.
    Peer
    This is a peer class.It acts like a client and a server at the same time.It reads server list(he is here too) and then he sends connections to others.
    Server
    Selector server for Peer.It accepts,reads and writes the response.IN ONE THREAD!
